                        <h3>Outcomes</h3>
                <p>
                     <h4> We will have increased enthusiasm among students regarding entrepreneurship
                            and give them a taste of the various processes that they might have to go
                            through during the industrial phase.</h4>
                    <ul class="middle">
                            
                                <li>Fund flow from various government and private investors.</li>
                                <li>Successful implementation of GEF’s “Inspire Innovate Incubate” Model.</li>
                                <li>Multidimensional skill development for students.</li>
                                <li>Development of Managerial, Administrative, leadership & Entrepreneurial
                                    qualities.</li>
                                <li>Maximum Media coverage as a part of Brand Building in International
                                    Level.</li>
                                <li>Techno-Entrepreneurship through creativity. Societal Impact.</li>
                                <li>Intangible outcomes such as Overall development of students, faculty and
                                    Institution.</li>
                                <li>Curriculum design under Project Based Learning</li>
                            
                        
                    </ul>
                </p>


